<div class="landing-page marble">
  <div class="blue-stripe text-center">
    <div class="half-buffer"></div>
    <div class="page-header-2">
      <h1>Sell Your House</h1>
      <h3 class="font-sans text-center">Make sure you get the most for your home.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="half-buffer"></div>
  </div> <!-- page header -->


  <div class="container background-transparent">
    <div class="half-buffer"></div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-8 background-transparent">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h2>Step 1: Take Our Prequalification Quiz</h2>
          <p>This basic information allows us to start researching what loans you qualify for financially.</p>
        </div> <!-- mini col -->

        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h2>Step 2: Provide Financial Information</h2>
          <p>To make the process as fast as possible, I need documents to verify your financial standing:
            <ul class="font-sans">
              <li>W2 forms for the past two years</li>
              <li>Current bank statements</li>
              <li>Any other relevant information about assets (the more documentation, the easier the process)</li>
              <li>Information to access credit score</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div> <!-- mini col -->

        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h2>Step 3: Get Your Loan Preapproval</h2>
          <p>This gives you the ability to go shop for houses knowing exactly what amount the bank will qualify you for.  No surprises!</p>
        </div> <!-- mini col -->

      </div> <!-- form -->

      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <div class="new-card border">
          <h3 class="text-center">Download a Free List of the Top 10 Mistakes Sellers Make</h3>
          <%= render partial: "layouts/new_subscriber", locals: { tags: "interest-selling, LM-mistakes-sellers-make" } %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- row -->
    <div class="buffer"></div>
  </div> <!-- container -->
</div> <!-- landing page -->
